race.comment: SPRING BREEZING (3) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (21.10) at this track in a NG. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. FIRST TRAIN OUT (1) copped a bump in the run last time and could manage only eighth (20.62) in a NG at Goulburn. Can do much better this time. BE WOWED (4) boasts a strong record this journey with 13 wins and six minors from 27 tries. Missed the frame latest (20.03) when fifth over 350m at Goulburn in a NG. Suited here and expected to run well. MOUNT FUJI (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
